title: The Regressor Protects Only Me
description: The Regressor Protects Only Me Manhwa Description: Humanity was designated as a disruptive species of the Cosmic Ecosystem. To reduce humanity’s numbers, the universe’s administrators initiate a survival game. Jin Jaehee, having returned from the final stage of the game, reaches one clear conclusion. “Kang Shion – only he can lead us to victory in this game.” Kang Shion, a genius with an unparalleled mind. Jin Jaehee, a regressor who lost in the survival game and returned to the past. With the regressor as his ally, Kang Shion begins to unravel the death game with unprecedented skill. 회귀자는 나만 지킨다
